Package main

Class Election

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.Election
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CPL_Election, IR_Election
    public class Election
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that represents an Election and contains methods set attributes of an election being the type, file name, file scanner, and number of total ballots.
